title: Fragrant citrus carrot cake
ingredients: ['90g wholemeal flour', '105g cake flour', '110g dark brown soft sugar', '1 tablespoon ground cinnamon', '1 tablespoon carob powder', '1 teaspoon baking powder', '1 teaspoon bicarbonate of soda', '1/2 teaspoon salt', '1 1/2 tablespoons treacle', '4 tablespoons vegetable oil', '2 eggs', '1 orange, juiced and zested', '1 1/2 teaspoons grated lemon zest', '80g raisins', '95g dried figs, chopped', '2 tablespoons poppy seeds', '270g grated carrots', '30g chopped pecans']
